# AWS Deployment Profile

This directory will contain the AWS deployment configuration for AI Shield Intelligence.

## Status

🚧 **Work in Progress** - Architecture design complete, implementation not yet started.

## Documentation

- **[aws-design_concept.md](aws-design_concept.md)** - Complete architecture design document including:
  - Intelligence source catalog (80+ sources)
  - AWS service architecture diagrams
  - Component specifications
  - Security and compliance requirements
  - Cost estimates and scaling plans
  - Implementation roadmap

## Planned Features

- Multi-AZ high availability deployment
- Auto-scaling based on workload
- Managed AWS services (RDS Aurora, ElastiCache, S3, Bedrock)
- CloudWatch monitoring and alerting
- VPC isolation and security groups
- Infrastructure as Code (Terraform/CDK)
- Multi-region support for data residency
- Enterprise-grade security and compliance

